# Configuration — copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is gitignored.
# Load before launching Jupyter:   set -a; source .env; set +a
#
# This repo needs no licensed services. An LLM API key is only used by optional
# notebook cells that call a hosted model for comparison — otherwise leave blank.

# ── Optional: a hosted LLM for comparison cells (any provider) ──
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
